@startuml Order Line Lifecycle - State Diagram
title Order Line Lifecycle (OrderLineStatus)

skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor #333333
}

state "PENDING" as PENDING
state "PREPARING" as PREPARING
state "COMPLETED" as COMPLETED
state "CANCELLED" as CANCELLED

[*] --> PENDING : createOrderLine

PENDING --> PREPARING : startPreparing

PENDING --> CANCELLED : cancelLine

PREPARING --> COMPLETED : complete

PREPARING --> CANCELLED : cancelLine

COMPLETED --> [*]

CANCELLED --> [*]

note bottom
  **createOrderLine** = thêm dòng order (một đợt món) → PENDING (trong code: OrderService.createOrderLine).
  **startPreparing** = bếp bắt đầu làm.
  **complete** = bếp hoàn thành dòng.
  **cancelLine** = hủy dòng order.
  ----
  Hiện tại code chỉ set PENDING khi tạo;
  PREPARING / COMPLETED / CANCELLED dùng khi triển khai luồng bếp.
end note

@enduml
